haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Augustus Kass
Fw Detlef Schwarzer
Fw Ruprecht Hess

 The mission was flown from Balatre aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 07/09/1916 near Moivrons.
A Nieuport 11.C1 of Esc N.68 was brought down by Tobias Klemme of Jasta 16b.
S/Lt Alfred Lafitte was killed in action.
Tobias Klemme was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.
